window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>New Easy Rawlins mysteriesâ€”original short stories from the <i>New York Times</i> bestselling and award-winning mystery author. As Carolyn See said in <i>The Washington Post Book World</i>: \"God bless the day that Walter Mosley created Easy Rawlins!\"<br> <br> This handsome collection contains six interconnected stories. Fans can now add these original stories in <i>Six Easy Pieces </i>to their Walter Mosley library: \"Smoke,\" \"Crimson Stain,\" \"Silver Lining,\" \"Lavender,\" \"Gato Green,\" \"Gray-Eyed Death,\" and \"Amber Gate.\"</p>"; 
